0d29			; 
0d29			; Multiply 8-bit value with a 16-bit value (right rotating) 
0d29			; In: Multiply A with DE 
0d29			;      Put lowest value in A for most efficient calculation 
0d29			; Out: HL = result 
0d29			; 
0d29			Mult12R: 
