1037			;Number in a to decimal ASCII 
1037			;adapted from 16 bit found in z80 Bits to 8 bit by Galandros 
1037			;Example: display a=56 as "056" 
1037			;input: a = number 
1037			;Output: a=0,value of a in the screen 
1037			;destroys af,bc (don't know about hl and de) 
1037			DispAToASCII: 
